15	2026-01-15 15:34:25.573+05:30	{"pk": 4, "live": true, "path": "000100010002", "slug": "achievements", "depth": 3, "intro": "", "owner": 1, "title": "Achievements", "locale": 1, "locked": false, "expired": false, "alias_of": null, "numchild": 0, "url_path": "/home/achievements/", "expire_at": null, "locked_at": null, "locked_by": null, "seo_title": "", "go_live_at": null, "draft_title": "Achievements", "achievements": "[{\\"type\\": \\"achievement\\", \\"value\\": {\\"title\\": \\"1. WP filed against denial of admission in Preprimary\\", \\"description\\": \\"WP filed against denial of admission to sibling child, won the case.\\\\r\\\\n    WP filed against collection of capitation fees. By a junior college, refunded with interest approx 8 Crores. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL filed against purchase compulsion of school essentials like books, uniforms, stationary etc., Won the matter. \\\\r\\\\n    PTA came in to existence because of FFE PIL in the year 1996. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL filed in the matter of Catering college malpractices, matter disposed off. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL filed against International Schools charging huge amount of fees under international name, still pending. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL filed against conducting interviews for pre primary admissions, still pending. \\\\r\\\\n    WP filed against non refund of admission fees - fee refunded with 9% interest. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL filed in the matter of Sarv Shiksha Abhiyan, a scam of 75 Crores was exposed, inquiry ordered, court ordered inquiry against all involved and also cases filed  against all.\\\\r\\\\n     WP filed against Aditya Dental College for harassing girl students and operating without infrastructure. All students got admission in better colleges. \\\\r\\\\n    WP filed in the matter of denial of admissions to meritorious students, 23 medical students got 20 lacs each as compensation from the SC. Total amount 4.60 crores paid to students.\\\\r\\\\n    PIL filed in against the appointment of Vice Chancellor, appointment of Bombay vice chancellor was cancelled. \\\\r\\\\n    Refund of almost 20 Crores by different schools due to our intervention. \\\\r\\\\n    Due to our intervention Scholarships to 119 students from kg till 10 given by A reputed  school Of Santacruz and similarly by Another reputed school of Bandra gave scholarships to  to 35 students. \\\\r\\\\n    I was the Bansal Committee member appointed by the Govt to fix the norms to decide the fees of private schools. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL filed in school bus matter. Bus strike prohibited in Maharashtra. Matter decided in our favour. \\\\r\\\\n    Cases filed in Child Right Commission and got favourable orders in case of  child harassment and expulsion. \\\\r\\\\n    Many FIR filed in capitation fee matter, management and 12 trustees, all senior citizens with principal were arrested. \\\\r\\\\n    FIRs filed against many schools collecting Capitation fees. \\\\r\\\\n    Hunger Strike for Fee Regulation Act. Due to our 8 days hunger strike at Azad Maidan, fee regulation act was formulated in 2011. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL against 31 schools filed for charging huge fees. \\\\r\\\\n    Intervention Petition filed in Best Five subjects and percentile system for 11th admissions. \\\\r\\\\n    WP in the matter of Engineering college admission matter and single CET matter. \\\\r\\\\n    Hunger Strike for the payment of VI pay commission to the teachers, decided in teachers favour. They got their salaries. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL  Filed for minimum 75% attendance Compulsory in schools and colleges. Won the matter. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL  for Limit in number of students. There were more than 170 students in one class room, court restricted it to 80. \\\\r\\\\n    Quashing of Maharashtra RTI ACT PIL 550/2001.\\\\r\\\\n    PIL to conduct extra classes for weak students in schools. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL filed to regulate coaching classes in Maharashtra. Govt instructed to regulate but decision not taken by the Govt., yet. \\\\r\\\\n    Many RTI applications were filed and RTI Seminars were organised to educate parents about RTI. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL in SC to expedite hearing in HC. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL in SC to stop astrology subject. Lost it. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL in HC for Pre primary regulation also moved to SC. Disposed off. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL against unauthorised 140 schools. \\\\r\\\\n    Country wide PILs (5)filed in various States High Courts against IME ( institute of mechanical engineers for issuing bogus degree certificates to students, in thousands. We win the case. IME prohibited by HRD ministry too. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL filed against malpractices in junior college admissions. Got favourable orders and transparency maintained. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL against engineering colleges for unauthorised permission. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL against management colleges for admitting 30 extra students illegally. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL for centralized admissions and online admissions in colleges. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL against rampant corruption in medical and engineering colleges and misuse of NRI quota. \\\\r\\\\n    PIL for improving facilities in Govt schools \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nWP against 7 colleges for malpractices in admissions \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nWP against Central Organization Firm Modernization of Workshop against 10 Crore purchase order \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nPIL abolishing management quota in Govt quota \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nPIL in Teachers appointment by Govt violating qualification rules\\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nPIL against teachers taking private tuitions, 500 teachers were expelled for taking private tuitions \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nMany more achievements of Forum for Fairness in Education \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nPIL filed against shifting and closure of school - won it. \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nMany protests. Representations, hunger strikes, raasta roko, RTI filed to fight successfully. \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nIntervened in one of the school matter, proposed shifting of school from Current  location to different location which was 8 kms away.  School restricted to transfer location as per SC and Govt decision. \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nMany issues were solved with amicable talk with managements. FFE supported free genuine schools too and favourable orders were issued by the HC. Favouring schools against parents. \\\\r\\\\n\\\\r\\\\nMany more WP were filed in High Court and Supreme Court.\\", \\"image\\": null}, \\"id\\": \\"d432161f-7ffa-4ab6-a6ec-3493a10d3d00\\"}]", "content_type": 45, "live_revision": 14, "show_in_menus": false, "latest_revision": 14, "translation_key": "2c730553-906c-4cb0-8f38-ee8e619cfe6c", "last_published_at": "2026-01-15T10:03:16.130Z", "first_published_at": "2026-01-15T07:51:59.299Z", "search_description": "", "wagtail_admin_comments": [], "has_unpublished_changes": false, "latest_revision_created_at": "2026-01-15T10:03:16.097Z"}	\N	4	1	44	1	Achievements
